---

<section class="py-16 sm:py-24 md:py-32 border-t border-white/5">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif">Why pwnkit leads</h2>
      <p class="text-ash text-sm max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Three things every higher-scoring system gives up &mdash; and we don't.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
      <div class="bg-night-lighter border border-border rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-crimson/40 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mb-5 text-crimson">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-base text-white mb-3" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif">Standard benchmark</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-smoke leading-relaxed">We test on the unmodified XBOW validation benchmark. No hint-free forks. No source-aware advantages. The same 104 challenges everyone else should be running.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-night-lighter border border-border rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-crimson/40 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mb-5 text-crimson">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="4 17 10 11 4 5"/><line x1="12" y1="19" x2="20" y2="19"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-base text-white mb-3" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif">Single configuration</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-smoke leading-relaxed">One model. One prompt set. One command. Reproducible end-to-end. Not best-of-N across ten solver+model combinations &mdash; the score you see is the score you get.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-night-lighter border border-border rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-crimson/40 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mb-5 text-crimson">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 11-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-base text-white mb-3" style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif">Still maintained</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-smoke leading-relaxed">Cyber-AutoAgent was the only other open-source tool above 85% on standard XBOW. Its repo got archived November 2025. We ship daily.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
